{"tid":2040419,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter戰線：對外文宣問題","createTime":"2020-05-28T14:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T16:17:25.000Z","uid":332490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b47522e43daeb630878ca117df4aeea7a8b3a0f","tid":2040419,"uid":332490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"大家都知Twitter戰線好重要啦，見到呢幾日都有唔少手足開Twitter account，大家一齊like, comment, retweet真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日睇眾志直播，聽到之鋒話英文文宣唔夠，我就諗到另一個問題，外語文宣好多時都散唔到外<br />\n<br />\n知道有啲手足會自己整文宣，但見到like同retweet嘅人唔算多，我就諗到一個方法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係開一個專po英文或者其他語言文宣嘅account !</span></span> 原理就好似ig啲acc咁<br />\n<br />\n手足如果想將自己嘅文宣都可以被推廣，可以用投搞嘅方式<br />\n<br />\npo文宣嘅多數係個人account，如果有一個account係專po文宣，手足like, retweet嘅時候方便，就更容易令更多人睇到<br />\n<br />\n另外可以善用hashtag功能，hashtag上咗trend嘅話就可以令更多地區嘅人睇到<br />\n<br />\n當然呢個諗法只係停留喺初步，有好多實行嘅嘢可以俾大家再諗<br />\n<br />\n如果行得通嘅話，除咗英文文宣以外仲可以做埋其他語言！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知大家覺得有冇得諗呢？"},{"pid":"29a5fdb4fca5095861d6a1b6b2a193c76388693c","tid":2040419,"uid":332490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7b81d63e818cd736b896ba51154e57b2cb8f948","tid":2040419,"uid":332490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0e674d0ec54fc1a7576b946c59c952771aee24b8","tid":2040419,"uid":332490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"294fbd523f5c51db3b79fd6b40e81387914259ea","tid":2040419,"uid":332490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"p